trans-unit.source: Specifies the state of an axis.
The AxisEnabled enumeration is used with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A> property to enable or disable an axis.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen AxisEnabled brukes med den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>til 책 aktivere eller deaktivere en akse.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A> property is set to Auto, an axis may or may not be displayed, depending on whether it is being used to plot a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>er satt til Auto, en akse kan eller kan ikke vises, avhengig av om den brukes til 책 tegne et <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: The axes that are used to plot data for a series are determined by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XAxisType%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YAxisType%2A> property settings.
trans-unit.target: Aksene som brukes til 책 tegne data for en serie, avhenger av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XAxisType%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YAxisType%2A>egenskapsinnstillingene.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YAxisType%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XAxisType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The axis is only enabled if it used to plot a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Aksen er bare aktivert hvis det brukes til 책 tegne et <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series"> </xref>.
